Additionally, the paper also involves techniques related to natural language processing and machine learning, which are relevant to sub-categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves statistical analysis, which is relevant to sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
